N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6170.7 - Liability

State Regulations

Nothing in this Part shall be construed as creating a cause
of action for damages or injunctive relief against the State or any of its
political subdivisions or officers or any agency thereof. Notes
